Her voice directly penetrated  my heart and those lyrics just amazing. 
'Dukhi jaage dukh de karan
Sukhi na jaage koi' 
lagi bina rain na jage koi
Personally connected..Will never forget..

snippet.textDisplay: At 00:15, the song bursts into full life with Sanam Marvi's voice... Full, open throated and deep and with a machine like yet human perfection, she perfects the entry to the song... while not strictly differentiated from a lot of the songs in the season, lagi bina holds you raptured for the first two minutes without any need for a single instrument... wish there was more usage of the powerhouse of a voice that sanam marvi brings to the table...
